Oh, good morning little friends,
your singing is oh so pretty.

00:09.677 --> 00:12.177
Yes, it is a very
beautiful day today,

00:12.179 --> 00:15.014
Certainly something
worth singing about.

00:15.016 --> 00:19.084
♪ there's music in the treetops
and there's music in the vale. ♪

00:19.086 --> 00:22.588
<i>♪ and all around me</i>
<i>music fills the sky ♪</i>

00:23.423 --> 00:25.457
<i>♪ there's music by the river</i>

00:25.459 --> 00:27.559
<i>♪ and there's music</i>
<i>in the grass ♪</i>

00:27.561 --> 00:32.197
<i>♪ and the music makes your</i>
<i>heart soar in reply ♪</i>

00:32.199 --> 00:35.134
<i>♪ aahhhh!</i>

00:35.136 --> 00:36.335
(growl)

00:36.337 --> 00:40.739
<i>♪ aaaaahhh!</i>

00:40.741 --> 00:43.042
<i>♪ ah ha ha! Ah ha ha!</i>

00:43.044 --> 00:47.613
<i>♪ aaaaah!</i>

00:47.615 --> 00:50.082
<i>♪ ah ha ha! Ah ha ha!</i>

00:50.084 --> 00:53.719
<i>♪ (ends on a sweet high</i>
<i>note) ♪</i>

00:53.721 --> 00:56.789
<i>(cheers)</i>

00:56.791 --> 01:00.459
Oh, thank you so much.
You're too kind.

01:01.428 --> 01:03.062
<i>Pinkie pie: Wow!</i>

01:05.832 --> 01:11.203
Oh. You um, you didn't
hear me, um ...

01:11.205 --> 01:13.539
Singing in the most
beautiful voice ever?

01:13.541 --> 01:15.140
Uh, yeah we did!

01:17.143 --> 01:18.410
<i>(whimper)</i>

01:21.548 --> 01:25.651
<i>♪ my little pony,</i>
<i>my little pony ♪</i>

01:25.653 --> 01:27.219
<i>♪ aaaaahhh!</i>

01:27.221 --> 01:32.157
<i>♪ I used to wonder what</i>
<i>friendship could be ♪</i>

01:32.159 --> 01:36.295
<i>♪ until you all shared</i>
<i>its magic with me ♪</i>

01:36.297 --> 01:37.429
<i>♪ big adventure</i>

01:37.431 --> 01:42.701
<i>♪ it's an easy feat</i>

01:42.703 --> 01:44.803
<i>♪ and magic makes it</i>
<i>all complete ♪</i>

01:44.805 --> 01:46.805
<i>♪ my little ponies</i>

01:46.807 --> 01:49.741
<i>♪ do you know you're all</i>
<i>my very best friends? ♪</i>

01:49.743 --> 01:52.377
♪

01:59.385 --> 02:03.722
Wow! I've never heard you
sing a solo like that before.

02:03.724 --> 02:06.492
It was like a little
slice of heaven.

02:06.494 --> 02:08.894
With ice cream on top!

02:08.896 --> 02:12.631
Fluttershy, I cannot believe
your spectacular voice

02:12.633 --> 02:15.467
Isn't part of the
pony tones quartet!

02:15.469 --> 02:17.503
Um...Well...I...

02:17.505 --> 02:22.374
For your ponyville pet center
fundraiser tomorrow night!

02:22.376 --> 02:24.676
Well, you see, I...

02:24.678 --> 02:27.212
This simply must be rectified!

02:27.214 --> 02:29.648
You must share that
stunning voice at the event.

02:29.650 --> 02:31.783
Yeah! It will be so amazing!

02:31.785 --> 02:34.486
You'd be there on stage,
basking in the hooflights,

02:34.488 --> 02:37.890
The center of attention,
a shining star...

02:37.892 --> 02:40.726
<i>With everypony staring</i>
<i>at you, judging you,</i>

02:40.728 --> 02:43.428
Jealously noting how they
could be way better than you.

02:43.430 --> 02:45.464
Why wasn't it them?
Why wasn't it them?

02:45.466 --> 02:47.666
<i>And then, when you choke,</i>
<i>they'll turn on you</i>

02:47.668 --> 02:49.535
Becoming a seething angry mob

02:49.537 --> 02:51.270
And you'll be horribly
humiliated,

02:51.272 --> 02:54.473
Never able to show your
face in ponyville again!

02:54.475 --> 02:58.310
Pinkie pie! Don't
be ridiculous!

02:58.312 --> 03:00.712
But I'm so good at it!

03:00.714 --> 03:02.614
Come, fluttershy.

03:02.616 --> 03:05.918
You will join the group making
the pony tones quartet

03:05.920 --> 03:08.320
The pony tones quintet!

03:08.322 --> 03:09.621
No!

03:09.623 --> 03:11.256
Pardon me?

03:11.258 --> 03:13.192
I love the pony tones.

03:13.194 --> 03:14.893
I'm one of their biggest fans.

03:14.895 --> 03:17.629
But I do not want to
perform with them.

03:17.631 --> 03:19.364
Why not, fluttershy?

03:19.366 --> 03:26.572
Well you see, I...I
have...Um...I-I have...

03:26.574 --> 03:28.307
Spit it out!

03:28.309 --> 03:31.343
I have...Stage fright!

03:31.345 --> 03:32.477
<i>(gasp)</i>

03:32.479 --> 03:33.845
Is it contagious?

03:33.847 --> 03:36.381
Stage fright isn't
a disease, pinkie.

03:36.383 --> 03:38.383
It just means that fluttershy
is scared to perform

03:38.385 --> 03:39.918
In front of everypony.

03:39.920 --> 03:41.687
I'm very thankful
the pony tones

03:41.689 --> 03:43.655
Are singing at the pet
center fundraiser.

03:43.657 --> 03:46.658
<i>And I'm really looking</i>
<i>forward to the performance.</i>

03:46.660 --> 03:49.728
But I'll be watching
safely from the audience.

03:49.730 --> 03:54.433
Well, I think it's a terrible
waste of an exquisite talent,

03:54.435 --> 03:56.501
But I understand that
you're not comfortable.

03:56.503 --> 03:58.370
Thank you.

03:58.372 --> 03:59.671
Ooh! Angel's right!

03:59.673 --> 04:03.642
There's a lot of work to
do before tomorrow's event!

04:06.379 --> 04:16.255
♪

04:16.257 --> 04:20.392
All right, pony tones, let's
run through that again!

04:20.394 --> 04:22.261
<i>(pitch pipe tone)</i>

04:22.263 --> 04:26.632
<i>♪ (doo wop bass notes)</i>

04:26.634 --> 04:31.036
<i>♪ (vocalizing in harmony)</i>

04:31.038 --> 04:35.440
♪ everypony's saying you should
<i>learn to express your voice. ♪</i>

04:35.442 --> 04:37.909
<i>♪ but if talk doesn't seem</i>
<i>like it's the answer ♪</i>

04:37.911 --> 04:44.850
<i>♪ when you find you've got the</i>
<i>music, got the music in you. ♪</i>

04:44.852 --> 04:50.389
<i>♪ find you've got the music</i>
<i>got the music in you. ♪</i>

04:50.391 --> 04:51.623
<i>(sigh)</i>

04:52.725 --> 04:54.393
Whoo hoo! Yeah!

04:54.395 --> 04:56.561
Rarity, you were awesome!

04:56.563 --> 04:59.831
Thank you, spike, but
this  <i>is</i> an ensemble.

05:01.734 --> 05:04.636
Enh, the rest of you
were pretty good, too.

05:04.638 --> 05:08.040
Oh, I thought you were all
amazing, pony tones.

05:08.042 --> 05:09.908
Thanks, fluttershy!

05:09.910 --> 05:12.477
Now, pony tones, I want you
all to rest your voices

05:12.479 --> 05:16.048
We'll do a final run-through
tomorrow before the big event.

05:16.050 --> 05:16.915
All right?

05:16.917 --> 05:17.949
Yup.

05:17.951 --> 05:22.454
Oh, rarity, the pony tones
are really going to make

05:22.456 --> 05:25.691
The ponyville pet center
fundraiser so special!

05:25.693 --> 05:29.328
Thank you so much for
helping me help the animals!

05:29.330 --> 05:32.364
Oh yes. It is wonderful
when a plan comes together

05:32.366 --> 05:34.833
Without any sort of
drama, isn't it?

05:34.835 --> 05:36.068
<i>(giggle)</i>

05:37.370 --> 05:39.071
<i>(owl hoots)</i>

05:39.073 --> 05:41.707
<i>(rooster crows)</i>

05:41.709 --> 05:55.620
♪

05:55.622 --> 05:57.122
Morning, fluttershy.

05:57.124 --> 05:59.358
Good morning,
pony tones!

05:59.360 --> 06:02.694
Actually, we're the pony
tones minus one tone.

06:02.696 --> 06:05.130
Big mac is
inconveniently late.

06:05.132 --> 06:06.565
<i>(galloping)</i>

06:06.567 --> 06:11.636
<i>(panting)</i>

06:11.638 --> 06:15.107
Have I not told you
about punctuality?

06:15.109 --> 06:17.442
Ah! I don't want
to hear it!

06:19.579 --> 06:21.446
<i>♪ (pitch pipe tone)</i>

06:21.448 --> 06:25.484
<i>♪ (no doo wop introduction)</i>

06:25.486 --> 06:26.651
(gulp)

06:29.622 --> 06:32.424
Big mac! Can you please
start the song?

06:33.926 --> 06:35.160
Nope.

06:35.162 --> 06:36.161
Big mac!

06:36.163 --> 06:37.496
Did you lose your voice?

06:37.498 --> 06:38.397
<i>(gulp)</i>

06:38.399 --> 06:39.598
Yup.

06:39.600 --> 06:40.665
<i>(gasps)</i>

06:43.936 --> 06:45.971
♪

06:45.973 --> 06:48.707
Whatever did you
do to cause this?

06:48.709 --> 06:50.041
Well...

06:51.879 --> 06:56.548
And welcome to the 12th annual
ponyville turkey call!

06:56.550 --> 06:58.450
<i>(cheering)</i>

06:58.452 --> 07:00.185
<i>(gobble)</i>

07:00.187 --> 07:01.887
Who will take the
title this year?

07:01.889 --> 07:06.725
Or will the turkey call
champion of six years

07:06.727 --> 07:11.096
<i>Defend his title to make</i>
<i>it lucky number seven?</i>

07:11.098 --> 07:13.732
We'll find out if
ya stop yer gabbin'

07:13.734 --> 07:16.034
And git on with
the gobblin'!

07:16.036 --> 07:17.736
All right, everypony!

07:17.738 --> 07:19.571
Let's talk turkey!

07:19.573 --> 07:21.973
Big mac, yer up!

07:21.975 --> 07:23.575
<i>(takes a deep breath)</i>

07:25.211 --> 07:27.979
A turkey call?

07:27.981 --> 07:31.850
You lost your voice
doing a...Turkey call?

07:31.852 --> 07:33.819
Lost his voice and the title!

07:33.821 --> 07:35.086
<i>(turkey call)</i>

07:36.689 --> 07:38.690
Now we can't
perform tonight.

07:38.692 --> 07:40.759
Wait! What? No!

07:42.162 --> 07:46.164
Otherwise the fundraiser
will be a disaster.

07:46.166 --> 07:49.034
Well, we cannot perform
tonight with only three voices.

07:49.036 --> 07:52.504
It would take rearranging
all the music

07:52.506 --> 07:55.907
<i>I'm sorry, fluttershy,</i>
<i>but I have no remedy</i>

07:55.909 --> 07:57.509
<i>For this situation.</i>

07:57.511 --> 07:58.844
<i>(gasp)</i>

07:58.846 --> 08:00.045
Of course!

08:00.047 --> 08:01.112
A remedy!

08:01.114 --> 08:02.180
Follow me!

08:08.254 --> 08:10.155
<i>(hoarse) ahhhh!</i>

08:10.157 --> 08:12.491
Hmmm.

08:12.493 --> 08:14.593
Aaahh.

08:15.995 --> 08:18.997
I can cure this
pony that is hoarse,

08:18.999 --> 08:21.700
But it will take
a longer course.

08:21.702 --> 08:23.101
Come again?

08:23.103 --> 08:27.272
I can mix a brew that
will work just right,

08:27.274 --> 08:29.841
But it cannot heal
him by tonight.

08:29.843 --> 08:33.578
Where are we ever going
to find a deep voice

08:33.580 --> 08:35.280
To replace big mac's?

08:35.282 --> 08:37.682
<i>(chuckle)</i>

08:37.684 --> 08:40.852
Pardon me, zecora,
but this is no laughing matter.

08:40.854 --> 08:43.088
We need a bass voice for
the harmonies to work!

08:43.090 --> 08:45.290
Without it, the
performance will be ruined!

08:45.292 --> 08:47.926
Please forgive my
strange elation,

08:47.928 --> 08:51.129
But I was not laughing
at your situation.

08:51.131 --> 08:56.067
Remember when you pony folk
stumbled into poison joke?

08:56.069 --> 08:59.137
<i>Miss fluttershy had</i>
<i>an unusual change,</i>

08:59.139 --> 09:01.540
<i>Deepening her vocal range.</i>

09:01.542 --> 09:03.842
(very low voice) I don't
want to talk about it.

09:05.312 --> 09:10.048
Your voice became really
low, making it sound like...

09:10.050 --> 09:11.883
Flutterguy!

09:11.885 --> 09:14.019
With these leaves,
I can mix a brew

09:14.021 --> 09:17.088
Creating the same
effect on you.

09:17.090 --> 09:18.990
Zecora, that's fantastic!

09:18.992 --> 09:20.892
Yes! I'll do it!

09:20.894 --> 09:23.328
I'd do anything for the animals!

09:23.330 --> 09:26.131
Why, you'd even
appear on stage!

09:26.133 --> 09:28.099
Oh, except that.

09:29.802 --> 09:31.870
I just can't bring
myself to sing on stage

09:31.872 --> 09:33.672
In front of everypony.

09:34.941 --> 09:38.276
What if you sang not
in front of everypony?

09:38.278 --> 09:42.814
What if big mac was on
stage moving his lips

09:42.816 --> 09:46.151
While you're behind the
curtain singing his part?

09:46.153 --> 09:48.186
It would be just like
singing in your house.

09:48.188 --> 09:50.255
<i>Nopony would know it was you.</i>

09:50.257 --> 09:53.291
Even still. I just don't think
I could sing in front of--

09:53.293 --> 09:55.827
You must! For the animals!

09:55.829 --> 09:58.597
<i>(squeaks)</i>

09:58.599 --> 10:04.369
Oh, ok, then...Mix it up.

10:04.371 --> 10:11.643
♪

10:11.645 --> 10:13.878
Now do it just
like we practiced.

10:14.981 --> 10:16.982
<i>(gasp)</i>

10:16.984 --> 10:25.657
<i>(crowd</i>
<i>chatters)</i>

10:25.659 --> 10:28.660
Good evening,
citizens of ponyville!

10:28.662 --> 10:30.829
I want to thank you all
for coming out tonight

10:30.831 --> 10:33.965
And generously supporting
the ponyville pet center!

10:33.967 --> 10:37.235
<i>Thanks to your kindness, pets</i>
<i>are finding loving homes</i>

10:37.237 --> 10:40.305
<i>And we are sure to meet</i>
<i>our fundraising goal!</i>

10:40.307 --> 10:41.806
Where's fluttershy?

10:41.808 --> 10:45.877
You know how much that
pony hates the spotlight.

10:45.879 --> 10:52.083
So, with no further ado, please
welcome...The pony tones!

10:52.085 --> 10:57.656
<i>(cheers)</i>

10:57.658 --> 10:58.823
<i>♪ (pitch pipe tone)</i>

10:58.825 --> 10:59.891
<i>(big inhale)</i>

10:59.893 --> 11:01.893
<i>(hoarse inhale)</i>

11:01.895 --> 11:06.431
