<i>♪ on every corner there's</i>
<i>a rhythm playing. ♪</i>

11:29.690 --> 11:33.925
<i>♪ then it happens suddenly</i>
<i>the music takes you over ♪</i>

11:33.927 --> 11:36.194
<i>♪ and you find you</i>
<i>got the music. ♪</i>

