would consider performing

13:04.084 --> 13:06.184
At my daughter
zippoorwhill's cuteciñera.

13:06.186 --> 13:07.418
Will you? Will you?

13:07.420 --> 13:08.787
We'd love to!

13:08.789 --> 13:09.921
When is it? Next week?

13:09.923 --> 13:10.989
Next month?

13:10.991 --> 13:12.123
Tomorrow!

13:13.993 --> 13:15.960
Oh, gracious, I'm
terribly sorry.

13:15.962 --> 13:18.163
That's just much
too last-minute.

13:18.165 --> 13:19.964
Oh no!

13:19.966 --> 13:21.900
Well...I understand.

13:21.902 --> 13:28.206
<i>♪ (sad tune)</i>

13:28.208 --> 13:32.377
We can't disappoint
that sweet little filly.

13:32.379 --> 13:34.179
Are you sure
you're up for it?

13:36.483 --> 13:39.884
<i>♪ when you find</i>
<i>you've got the music, ♪</i>

13:39.886 --> 13:46.257
<i>♪ find you've got the music,</i>
<i>got the music in you ♪</i>

13:46.259 --> 13:51.296
<i>♪ got the music, got</i>
<i>the music in you. ♪</i>

13:51.298 --> 13:52.864
Whoo yeah!

13:52.866 --> 13:54.165
Yeah! We got the pony tones!

13:54.167 --> 13:55.400
We got the pony tones!

14:01.040 --> 14:03.208
Amazing pony tones!

14:03.210 --> 14:05.543
And it would be even more
amazing if you could perform

14:05.545 --> 14:08.313
At my ribbon-cutting
ceremony tomorrow!

14:09.415 --> 14:12.283
Oh, mayor, we would
love to but...

14:14.620 --> 14:17.488
Will you excuse us
for a second, mayor?

14:17.490 --> 14:18.890
Certainly.

14:21.293 --> 14:22.861
(softly) don't
worry, fluttershy.

14:22.863 --> 14:27.465
(deep voice) but we wouldn't
want to disappoint the mayor.

14:29.869 --> 14:34.639
Well then mayor, the pony tones
will happily perform

14:34.641 --> 14:35.506
At your ceremony!

14:40.312 --> 14:44.883
<i>♪ (doowop introduction)</i>

14:44.885 --> 14:47.085
<i>♪ it's hot outside and</i>
<i>you see the sunshine. ♪</i>

14:47.087 --> 14:49.254
<i>♪ something's in the</i>
