14:49.256 --> 14:51.489
<i>♪ sky is clear and</i>
<i>you're feeling so fine. ♪</i>

14:51.491 --> 14:53.925
<i>♪ everything's going</i>
<i>to be a-ok. ♪</i>

14:53.927 --> 15:00.098
♪

15:00.100 --> 15:02.901
You wouldn't want to
disappoint the spa patrons.

15:02.903 --> 15:07.972
<i>♪ (singing continues)</i>

15:07.974 --> 15:12.410
<i>♪ on every corner there's</i>
<i>a rhythm playing. ♪</i>

15:12.412 --> 15:15.546
<i>♪ then it happens suddenly</i>
<i>the music takes you over ♪</i>

15:15.548 --> 15:17.348
We wouldn't want to disappoint
the school ponies.

15:17.350 --> 15:20.018
<i>♪ and you find you</i>
<i>got the music. ♪</i>

15:20.020 --> 15:26.224
<i>♪ find you've got the music</i>
<i>got the music in you. ♪</i>

15:26.226 --> 15:30.962
<i>♪ got the music! Got</i>
<i>the music in you! ♪</i>

15:30.964 --> 15:33.698
<i>(cheers)</i>

15:43.375 --> 15:46.044
Fluttershy! We
must talk to you.

15:46.046 --> 15:47.512
Big mac's voice
is all better.

15:47.514 --> 15:49.213
Yup.

15:52.451 --> 15:55.086
Now you can bathe in the
poison joke antidote

15:55.088 --> 15:57.388
And sound like your
lovely self again!

15:58.490 --> 16:01.426
It's just...I didn't know
that last performance

16:01.428 --> 16:04.362
Was mylast  performance.

16:06.565 --> 16:08.199
Fluttershy! Stop!

16:10.369 --> 16:13.538
Would it be ok if fluttershy
sang for you one last time?

16:16.508 --> 16:18.376
Yup.

16:24.149 --> 16:26.351
<i>♪ (fluttershy improvising)</i>

16:26.353 --> 16:30.555
<i>Hey-o, you can find it, find</i>
<i>it in your heart yeah yeah!</i>

16:30.557 --> 16:33.358
<i>♪ find the music yeah yeah,</i>

16:33.360 --> 16:39.497
<i>♪ it's in you right now,</i>
<i>oh yeah, ♪</i>

16:39.499 --> 16:47.638
<i>♪ you can find the music,</i>
<i>I love the music yeah! ♪</i>

16:47.640 --> 16:49.307
All: Fluttershy?

16:54.546 --> 16:57.281
<i>(teeth chattering)</i>

16:57.283 --> 17:00.785
<i>(screaming cheers)</i>

17:00.787 --> 17:11.129
<i>(horror sound effects)</i>

17:11.131 --> 17:13.398
<i>(frightened shouts)</i>

17:14.434 --> 17:17.535
You got some 'splainin' to do!

17:17.537 --> 17:18.636
Yup.
Turkey call?

17:18.638 --> 17:20.204
Yup.
Trash yer voice?

17:20.206 --> 17:21.472
Yup.
Zecora remedy?

17:21.474 --> 17:22.640
Nope.
Not quick enough?

17:22.642 --> 17:24.375
Yup.
Needed a deep voice?

17:24.377 --> 17:25.410
Yup.
Poison joke?

17:25.412 --> 17:26.377
Yup.
Flutterguy?

17:26.379 --> 17:29.480
And that shy filly was living
her dream in the shadows

17:29.482 --> 17:31.049
Because she couldn't
bring herself

17:31.051 --> 17:32.216
To come into the
spotlight?

17:32.218 --> 17:33.217
Yup.

17:33.219 --> 17:34.585
Well, for corn's sake!

17:34.587 --> 17:35.820
Let's go!

17:37.423 --> 17:39.223
<i>Twilight: Fluttershy?</i>

17:39.225 --> 17:40.658
You in here?

17:40.660 --> 17:42.326
Yes.

17:42.328 --> 17:45.596
<i>Pinkie: That was</i>
<i>totally unbelievable!</i>

17:45.598 --> 17:48.232
I mean, the curtain came
up, and there you were,

17:48.234 --> 17:50.201
Singing in front of everypony!

17:50.203 --> 17:52.403
And, you know, I don't think
any pony was jealous

17:52.405 --> 17:54.572
Cause there certainly
wasn't an angry mob!

17:54.574 --> 17:56.841
But it must have been horrible
standing there on stage!

17:56.843 --> 17:59.644
All eyes glued directly on you.

17:59.646 --> 18:03.347
It's like you were living your
own personal worst nightmare!

18:03.349 --> 18:05.183
<i>(sobbing)</i>

18:05.185 --> 18:06.350
It was!

18:06.352 --> 18:09.754
(frantic sobbing)

18:11.090 --> 18:12.857
What? Too much?

18:12.859 --> 18:17.728
What pinkie meant to say was
that you were really great.

18:17.730 --> 18:19.564
Wait! Didn't I say that?

18:19.566 --> 18:21.265
Hardly!

18:21.267 --> 18:24.102
You were great!

18:24.104 --> 18:26.637
You totally blew
my mind!

18:27.806 --> 18:29.340
Incredible!

18:29.342 --> 18:34.512
Though, no offence, you
kind of sounded like a dude.

18:34.514 --> 18:35.746
<i>(sobs)</i>

18:37.182 --> 18:39.150
A great sounding dude!

18:42.387 --> 18:44.522
Well, thank you all.

18:44.524 --> 18:46.157
I'm glad you enjoyed it...

18:48.293 --> 18:50.795
...Because I'm never going to
sing in front of anypony

18:50.797 --> 18:52.463
Ever again.

18:52.465 --> 18:53.364
<i>(gasp)</i>

18:53.366 --> 18:55.533
Are you kidding me?

18:55.535 --> 18:57.502
Can we please
stop running!

18:57.504 --> 19:00.905
<i>(panting)</i>

19:00.907 --> 19:04.308
I just don't understand
why, fluttershy.

19:04.310 --> 19:06.677
<i>After all, you're the one</i>
<i>that wanted the pony tones</i>

19:06.679 --> 19:10.281
To sing for every silly
thing that was requested of us.

19:10.283 --> 19:13.618
You mean, you knew I
really wanted to perform?

19:13.620 --> 19:15.253
Of course I knew!

19:15.255 --> 19:20.658
And for all her babbling, pinkie
pie was right about one thing.

19:20.660 --> 19:26.264
When that curtain fell, and
everypony saw you singing,

19:26.266 --> 19:29.333
You lived your worst nightmare.

19:29.335 --> 19:30.935
Was it really that bad?

19:30.937 --> 19:32.403
Yes!

19:32.405 --> 19:34.505
Well, what was so bad about it?

19:34.507 --> 19:36.307
The thunderous
applause?

19:36.309 --> 19:38.509
The praise for your
fantastic singin'?

19:38.511 --> 19:40.945
The screaming fans?

19:49.821 --> 19:53.891
♪ there's music in the treetops
and there's music in the vale ♪

19:53.893 --> 19:58.362
<i>♪ and all around the</i>
<i>music fills the sky. ♪</i>

19:58.364 --> 20:02.667
♪ there's music by the river and
<i>there's music in the grass. ♪</i>

20:02.669 --> 20:06.971
<i>♪ and the music makes your</i>
<i>heart soar into flight. ♪</i>

20:06.973 --> 20:10.308
<i>When you find you've</i>
<i>got the music,</i>

20:10.310 --> 20:12.443
<i>♪ you've got to look</i>
<i>inside and find. ♪</i>

20:12.445 --> 20:14.412
<i>♪ find you've got the music</i>

20:14.414 --> 20:16.547
<i>♪ the music deep inside you.</i>

20:16.549 --> 20:18.649
<i>♪ find you've got the music.</i>

20:18.651 --> 20:23.387
<i>♪ cause when you look</i>
<i>inside you'll see it. ♪</i>

20:23.389 --> 20:26.958
<i>♪ you're going to find,</i>
<i>you're going to find. ♪</i>

20:26.960 --> 20:31.862
<i>♪ got the music, got</i>
<i>the music...In you! ♪</i>

20:31.864 --> 20:37.702
<i>(cheers)</i>

20:37.704 --> 20:39.637
You did it,
fluttershy!

20:39.639 --> 20:41.639
See? That
wasn't so bad.

20:41.641 --> 20:43.641
And you didn't look completely
petrified by the fact

20:43.643 --> 20:45.643
That we're all staring
at you at all!

20:47.679 --> 20:48.846
How do you feel?

20:48.848 --> 20:51.782
Surprisingly ok!

20:51.784 --> 20:55.319
Because the pony tones
have been booked for the

20:55.321 --> 20:58.623
Apple family's zap apple
jam extraordinaire!

20:58.625 --> 21:01.592
Oh no! I couldn't
do that!

21:03.962 --> 21:04.895
Why not?

21:04.897 --> 21:05.730
How come?

21:05.732 --> 21:06.697
Seriously?

21:06.699 --> 21:10.701
But for now, baby
steps, everypony.

21:10.703 --> 21:11.902
Baby steps.

21:13.939 --> 21:16.741
<i>Fluttershy: Sometimes</i>
<i>being afraid can stop you</i>

21:16.743 --> 21:19.343
<i>From doing something</i>
<i>that you love.</i>

21:19.345 --> 21:21.646
<i>But hiding behind these fears</i>
<i>means you're only hiding</i>

21:21.648 --> 21:23.781
<i>From your true self.</i>

21:23.783 --> 21:25.716
<i>It's much better to</i>
<i>face those fears</i>

21:25.718 --> 21:30.521
So you can shine and be the best
<i>pony you can possibly be!</i>
